# Responsive Design Fixes - Summary

## What Was Done

### 1. Created Comprehensive Responsive Utility Hook ✅
**File:** `src/utils/useResponsive.js`

A new comprehensive responsive utility hook that provides:
- Device type detection (small/medium/large phones, tablets)
- Android-specific device detection
- Consistent scaling functions (scale, verticalScale, moderateScale)
- Responsive font sizing
- Responsive spacing
- Grid layout helpers (getColumns, getCardWidth)
- Landscape detection
- Pixel ratio support

**Usage:**
```javascript
import { useResponsive } from '../utils/useResponsive';

const MyScreen = () => {
    const { 
        width, height, 
        scale, fontSize, spacing,
        isTablet, isAndroidSmall,
        getColumns, getCardWidth 
    } = useResponsive();
    
    // Use in styles
    const styles = StyleSheet.create({
        title: { fontSize: fontSize(24), padding: spacing(16) }
    });
};
```

